  "detailed_description": "<h1>My next game</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757860/extras/0e6577a49583252a0906fb3895de3df9.poster.avif?t=1724994202\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757860/extras/0e6577a49583252a0906fb3895de3df9.webm?t=1724994202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757860/extras/0e6577a49583252a0906fb3895de3df9.mp4?t=1724994202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Relaxing and simple short game about flying in abstract, peaceful environment. <br><br>Play as a bubble, follow the coloured tape to reach the main bubble.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique calming, peaceful game.<br></li><li>Abstract and colourful gaming environment.<br></li><li>Relaxing sound atmosphere.<br></li><li>Simple and intuitive gaming experience.<br></li><li>Alternative psychedelic display mode.<br></li><li>No stories, just flying and lots of bubbles!</li></ul>",
